Shhh… not everything in Vegas is loud🤫 Hidden beneath the Mob Museum is @mobmuseum_underground — a Prohibition-style speakeasy serving up vintage vibes, handcrafted cocktails, and history in every sip✨
From the secret entrance to the 1920s-inspired drinks, it felt like stepping back in time⌛️
Whether you’re a history buff or just love an aesthetic night out, this place is a total must-visit when you’re in Vegas.

Wearing @risate.clothing🤎

I was hosted here and honestly, it’s such a cool hidden gem.
10/10 for the vibe, the drinks, and the overall experience🤌🏻 Would you have snuck into a speakeasy back in the day?
